  <main>
    <section class="hero">
      <div class="hero-title">AI for Water Pollution Detection</div>
      <p class="hero-subtitle">
        AquaLens AI uses deep learning and computer vision to classify water images as <strong>clean</strong> or
        <strong>polluted</strong>, providing a fast and scalable tool for environmental monitoring.
      </p>

      <div class="badge-row">
        <span class="badge">Computer Vision</span>
        <span class="badge">AlexNet ¬∑ VGG16 ¬∑ ResNet18</span>
